      "side": 1,
      "message": "This had been is_posix, but now that it’s crashpad_is_posix, I can’t see that from here.\n\nI don’t want to import crashpad_dependencies.gni here in BUILDCONFIG.gn, because that exposes it everywhere without an explicit import. Also, it’d require contortions in ordering here: crashpad_dependencies.gni uses executable_configs, which isn’t set until later in this file. Pulling crashpad_is_posix out into its own is_posix.gni doesn’t really help because its definition still depends on crashpad_dependencies.",
