      "message": "Could we make is_clang non-global?\n\nOtherwise, I guess we could try deferring the determination of the value of is_clang until later, by doing something like defaulting is_clang to an \"unknown\" -1 and then having an import determine the real value later when the values on which you want to have the default value depend, are available.",
